                Goliath Film & Media Holdings is a development stage company which plans to engage in developing and licensing distribution of video content of film and television content. It operates through its wholly-owned subsidiary Goliath Film and Media International. The company was founded on February 16, 2010 and is headquartered in Marina del Rey, CA.
            




